  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seed Hunter is an action-packed Roguelite game. We strive to incorporate handcrafted animations, traditional Chinese gameplay design, and a variety of items and weapon choices. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/125cb5b19360ee5091655b7a32082600.poster.avif?t=1763376128\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/125cb5b19360ee5091655b7a32082600.webm?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/125cb5b19360ee5091655b7a32082600.mp4?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >7 Types and 37 Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Axe, Sword & Shield, Dual Blades, Great Sword, Sword, Kunai, and Bow. We offer 37 different weapons across 7 categories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4ce4cd0a3a3ed5b0640d2b33413ca2b2.poster.avif?t=1763376128\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4ce4cd0a3a3ed5b0640d2b33413ca2b2.webm?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4ce4cd0a3a3ed5b0640d2b33413ca2b2.mp4?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For each weapon, you will have different skills. If you like it, why not make it stronger and play with it the way you enjoy? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hundreds of Ability Cards, 8 Upgrade Paths</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have designed two different skill trees. You can add some skills from your base, which will make you stronger in your next adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For your adventure, we have created more than 100 different skill cards that provide you with unlimited play styles, making you the strongest hunter we have ever seen. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4d793469fdb4eb83fd19ac5acc8361f3.poster.avif?t=1763376128\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4d793469fdb4eb83fd19ac5acc8361f3.webm?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4d793469fdb4eb83fd19ac5acc8361f3.mp4?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Handcraft Animation in Seed Hunter</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Like our favorite game, Cuphead, we use handcrafted animation in Seed Hunter. We create every jump and slash ourselves from scratch. We hope it provides you with a splendid gaming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/160cd58a2cab72ed4972a7c1daa064f0.poster.avif?t=1763376128\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/160cd58a2cab72ed4972a7c1daa064f0.webm?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/160cd58a2cab72ed4972a7c1daa064f0.mp4?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seed Hunter is an action-packed Roguelite game. We strive to incorporate handcrafted animations, traditional Chinese gameplay design, and a variety of items and weapon choices. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/125cb5b19360ee5091655b7a32082600.poster.avif?t=1763376128\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/125cb5b19360ee5091655b7a32082600.webm?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/125cb5b19360ee5091655b7a32082600.mp4?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >7 Types and 37 Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Axe, Sword & Shield, Dual Blades, Great Sword, Sword, Kunai, and Bow. We offer 37 different weapons across 7 categories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4ce4cd0a3a3ed5b0640d2b33413ca2b2.poster.avif?t=1763376128\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4ce4cd0a3a3ed5b0640d2b33413ca2b2.webm?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4ce4cd0a3a3ed5b0640d2b33413ca2b2.mp4?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For each weapon, you will have different skills. If you like it, why not make it stronger and play with it the way you enjoy? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hundreds of Ability Cards, 8 Upgrade Paths</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have designed two different skill trees. You can add some skills from your base, which will make you stronger in your next adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For your adventure, we have created more than 100 different skill cards that provide you with unlimited play styles, making you the strongest hunter we have ever seen. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4d793469fdb4eb83fd19ac5acc8361f3.poster.avif?t=1763376128\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4d793469fdb4eb83fd19ac5acc8361f3.webm?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/4d793469fdb4eb83fd19ac5acc8361f3.mp4?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Handcraft Animation in Seed Hunter</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Like our favorite game, Cuphead, we use handcrafted animation in Seed Hunter. We create every jump and slash ourselves from scratch. We hope it provides you with a splendid gaming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/160cd58a2cab72ed4972a7c1daa064f0.poster.avif?t=1763376128\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/160cd58a2cab72ed4972a7c1daa064f0.webm?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1078490/extras/160cd58a2cab72ed4972a7c1daa064f0.mp4?t=1763376128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
